KitKat took damage from the fight. Then Destructor grabbed her and 
flew off to the new base.  Right Now, KitKat is dented up, has holes 
in her armor and is leaking. But she has business to attend to before 
she can get tot he CR tank. GoldenEye and Terrorsaur are still at the 
fight scene. I'm sure if Quickstrike is there or not. The tretreat 
happened so fast, I hardly had time to keep up. I'm sorry KSLawdogg, 
it kind of got away from me.  Ah, but yes, KitKat did take on damage.
